/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Introduction rule to prove that `b` is the infimum of `s`: it suffices to check that `b`\nis smaller than all elements of `s`, and that this is not the case of any `w>b`.\nSee `sInf_eq_of_forall_ge_of_forall_gt_exists_lt` for a version in complete lattices. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Order/ConditionallyCompletePartialOrder/Basic.html#DirectedOn.csInf_eq_of_forall_ge_of_forall_gt_exists_lt","kind":"theorem","line":92,"name":"DirectedOn.csInf_eq_of_forall_ge_of_forall_gt_exists_lt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Order/ConditionallyCompletePartialOrder/Basic.lean#L92-L95"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Order/ConditionallyCompletePartialOrder/Basic.html#DirectedOn.csSup_eq_of_forall_le_of_forall_lt_exists_gt\"><span class=\"name\">DirectedOn</span>.<span class=\"name\">csSup_eq_of_forall_le_of_forall_lt_exists_gt</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/ConditionallyCompletePartialOrder/Defs.html#ConditionallyCompletePartialOrderSup\">ConditionallyCompletePartialOrderSup</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"d